{"tid":1246632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想係度呼籲今日仲肯出黎既戰友","createTime":"2019-06-20T20:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T00:30:23.000Z","uid":114186,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8d699b426880e4a7eb0e7eff60a341026b56c3","tid":1246632,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:39:47.000Z","msg":"無論幾困難 都要用愛香港既心去繼續抗爭<br />\n今日仲肯出黎既人 應該深深明白自由民主既可貴<br />\n但萬一呢次輸左 請大家積極考慮移民<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港已經無得救!</span></strong></span><br />\n啲港豬咁天真信林鄭個仆街暫緩即係唔會再推<br />\n並見到港共各部門咁腐敗都唔出黎 <br />\n相反到依家仲掛住吃喝玩樂既話<br />\n佢地就自己承擔返個後果 <br />\n我唔想大家同啲死港豬攬埋一齊死"},{"pid":"e47caa1c92dfdb7c4e5199073796516d8adba842","tid":1246632,"uid":202730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:40:34.000Z","msg":"又分化 3毛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eab9ae1ead818579d0bbda562905142f1a8247","tid":1246632,"uid":75156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:41:12.000Z","msg":"梁天琦都入左去坐 仲有藉口逃避？"},{"pid":"3ab26c2d59c29fa7d816e7088f24f20e4d13d426","tid":1246632,"uid":84355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:41:16.000Z","msg":"叮 三毛已到帳 請查收"},{"pid":"6c9de90caebf1927584e23aeb97097217b03ad7f","tid":1246632,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"香港人嘅潛能仲未逼晒出嚟<br />\n香港仲有得打"},{"pid":"7a8e70fced543b4148996c8a7f108188919a7ad7","tid":1246632,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c9de90caebf1927584e23aeb97097217b03ad7f","tid":1246632,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"香港人嘅潛能仲未逼晒出嚟<br />\n香港仲有得打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:45:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得你高估左啲港豬<br />\n我亦無叫大家放棄"},{"pid":"e0d70a9d47d32478888fd1be2bebcb51497de656","tid":1246632,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c9de90cae